         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Ö Apollodoros and Herakleides. Petosiris the sitologos Ö of Agema, reports that 12 1/2 artabas have been measured out to him by N.N. son of Epidiktos, kleros-holder, for the Ö of the 31st year, total 12 1/2 artabas. The 31st year, Mesore 19th.</ab>
